@startuml SequenceDiagram_DataBinding
title Sequence Diagram — Two-Way Data Binding\nUpload photo → INotifyPropertyChanged → DataGridView auto-update

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor White

actor "User" as User

participant ": FormMain"                              as FM
participant ": CachingFacebookProxy"                  as Proxy
participant "vm : AlbumViewModel"                     as VM
participant "m_AlbumBindingList : BindingList<AlbumViewModel>" as BL
participant ": DataGridView"                          as Grid
participant ": FacebookService"                       as SDK

note over BL, Grid
  Setup (once at startup):
  DataGridView.DataSource = m_AlbumBindingList
  Columns bound via DataPropertyName = "Name" / "PhotoCount"
end note

== Load albums (BackgroundWorker — background thread) ==

User  ->  FM  : buttonLoadAlbums_Click()
activate FM

loop for each album
    FM ->  VM  : new AlbumViewModel { Name, PhotoCount }
    activate VM
    FM ->  BL  : m_AlbumBindingList.Add(vm)
    activate BL
    BL --> Grid : ListChanged event → row added automatically
    deactivate BL
    deactivate VM
end

deactivate FM

== Upload photo → targeted single-cell update ==

User  ->  FM   : buttonUploadPhoto_Click()
activate FM
FM    ->  Proxy : UploadPhotoToAlbum(album, filePath)
activate Proxy
Proxy ->  SDK   : [Graph API upload — takes time]
activate SDK
SDK  --> Proxy  : success
deactivate SDK
Proxy ->  Proxy : r_CachedAlbumPhotos.Remove(albumId)
Proxy --> FM    : success
deactivate Proxy

FM    ->  Proxy : GetPhotosFromAlbum(album)
activate Proxy
Proxy -->  FM   : List<Photo> (fresh — cache was cleared)
deactivate Proxy

FM    ->  VM   : m_AlbumBindingList[index].PhotoCount = newCount
activate VM

note over VM
  PhotoCount setter fires:
  onPropertyChanged("PhotoCount")
  → PropertyChanged event raised
end note

VM    ->  BL   : PropertyChanged event
activate BL
BL    ->  Grid : notify: cell [index, "PhotoCount"] changed
activate Grid
Grid --> User  : single cell updated in-place\n(no full reload)
deactivate Grid
deactivate BL
deactivate VM
deactivate FM
@enduml
